commands.value: Software Engineer skilled in automation testing using Selenium, TestNG, and Cucumber (BDD). Skilled in functional and API testing, developing and executing automation scripts, validating workflows, and tracking defects using Asana and Jira. Chrome browser automation in both headed and headless modes. Familiar with Agile practices. Work Experience Software Engineer | Ticking Minds Technology Solutions Pvt. Ltd., Chennai | March 2025 – Present MAF Application (Automation Scripts & BDD) July 2025-Sep 2025 Developed and executed automation scripts for reject, recycle, and reversal dates using Selenium, Java, TestNG, and Cucumber (BDD). Wrote feature files for BDD scenarios to implement test workflows. Verified automation outcomes against expected results. Reported and tracked defects using Jira. Automated test cases in MAF applications executed in Chrome (headed and headless modes) VistaFlow –HRMS Application (User Service Module) April 2025-July 2025 Tested user functionalities related to role-based access and authentication for HR and Admin roles and user. Performed manual testing, wrote and executed detailed test cases, and tracked defects. Conducted API testing using Postman for endpoints relevant to assigned modules. Verified role-based access control and authentication workflows. Logged and monitored defects using Asana for timely resolution. OATS Tools(Orthogonal Array Test Generator) – API Testing April 2025 Developed an Orthogonal Array Test Generator for API testing, dynamically generating test combinations using Factors, Levels, and OA types (L4, L8, L9, etc.). Executed API calls and validated responses against expected outputs. Integrated Allure Reports to display detailed results, improving test coverage and efficiency. Skills Automation & Programming: Core Java, Selenium WebDriver, TestNG, Cucumber (BDD). API Testing: Postman, Rest Assured (Java-based API automation). Database: MySQL. Version Control & Code Quality: GitLab, SonarQube. Manual Testing & Validation: Functional testing, field validation, regression testing, test case design, defect reporting. Reporting & Test Management: Allure Reports, Jira, Asana. Build & Dependency Management: Maven. Education Bachelor of Technology (B.Tech) in Information Technology Sri Sairam Institute of Technology, Chennai CGPA: 9.0| Graduated: 2024 Certificates SQL-Skillrack Java
